estuary-theatre%2Ftesting%2Fall_key_type.Query:
MERGE INTO `estuary-theatre`.testing.all_key_types_part_one AS l
USING flow_temp_table_7 AS r
ON 
	l.id = r.c0 AND l.id >= 1 AND l.id <= 1
	AND l.strintkey = r.c1 AND l.strintkey >= '10' AND l.strintkey <= '10'
	AND l.strnumkey = r.c2 AND l.strnumkey >= '10.1' AND l.strnumkey <= '10.1'
WHEN MATCHED AND r._flow_delete THEN
	DELETE
WHEN MATCHED THEN
	UPDATE SET l.counter = r.c3, l.flow_published_at = r.c4, l.strint = r.c5, l.strnum = r.c6
WHEN NOT MATCHED AND NOT r._flow_delete THEN
	INSERT (id, strintkey, strnumkey, counter, flow_published_at, strint, strnum)
	VALUES (r.c0, r.c1, r.c2, r.c3, r.c4, r.c5, r.c6);
